Package game.economy.runes.manager

Class DroppedRuneManager

java.lang.Object
game.economy.runes.manager.DroppedRuneManager
public class DroppedRuneManager
extends java.lang.Object
Handles dropped runes. Now many actors can drop runes as they wish. When rest is called, this will protect runes by setting enum.
Author:
Kok Tim Ming
